{"tid":1016501,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[冷戰] 一次鮮為人知的叛逃事件，改變了冷戰局勢","createTime":"2019-02-10T18:34:03.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-13T10:17:50.000Z","uid":52658,"like":14,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":25,"replies":[{"pid":"f111a82205fb78446f415b80124cb153e617f329","tid":1016501,"uid":52658,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-10T18:34:03.000Z","msg":"1976年9月6日，蘇聯國土防空軍精銳部隊513團在例行的編隊訓練時，駕駛MIG-25的維克托&middot;別連科突然消失在編隊中，包含友機和地面人員都以為別連科以及失控墜海<br />\n<br />\n但實際上別連科早已成功避開友機和地面雷達，以貼地30-60公尺的高度朝距離蘇聯約700公里的日本飛行。 但別連科為躲避蘇聯雷達所採取的低空飛行，讓航程原本就不長的MIG-25帶來額外的燃油消耗<br />\n<br />\n因此別連科也沒把握剩餘的燃料能否支持他飛到日本，直到距離蘇聯雷達約320公里處時，別連科認為自己已經擺脫蘇聯雷達的追蹤而抬升飛行高度<br />\n<br />\n雖然他的確沒被蘇聯的雷達抓到，但也因此被日本的雷達掃描到。 發現不明飛行物接近的日本自衛隊立刻派出戰機攔截<br />\n<br />\n自衛隊的戰機也無法以速度著稱的MIG-25。但當別連科接近日本本島時，機上的燃料警示燈卻亮起，於是別連科決定轉向較近的北海道函館民用機場<br />\n<br />\n在經歷不成功的一次降落後，別連科第二次終於成功駕駛燃料即將用光的MIG-25降落<br />\n<br />\n雖然函館機場的跑道長度不足，讓別連科的MIG-25衝出跑道還順便爆了個輪胎。"},{"pid":"2965e411d32dace318ef090063ccf947ee56a73c","tid":1016501,"uid":52658,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-10T18:35:44.000Z","msg":"當別連科打開座艙蓋時，突然大聲喝斥上前圍觀的日本人別拍照，但大部分的日本人顯然聽不懂俄語，逼得別連科拔槍朝天空射兩槍才趕走群眾<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n這時別連科也才發現自己居然照著平常的訓練SOP走，接著他才將寫下「趕快聯絡美國CIA」的紙條給揮著白旗的機場官員。 <br />\n<br />\n美國得知別連科駕著MIG-25叛逃日本的消息後<span style=\"color: red;\">龍心</span>大悅，但蘇聯的面子卻因此差點丟光<br />\n<br />\n因為用現在的形容詞來說，蘇聯可說是「看報紙才知道」別連科叛逃的消息，為了挽回面子，蘇聯起初還聲稱別連科是因為「戰機故障不得不降落在日本，還為保護戰機而被日本扣留」<br />\n<br />\n蘇聯還以這名義要求日本放人放機，之後更加戲開了記者會，找來別連科的妻子和母親哭訴「我等著你回來」。 <br />\n<br />\n沒想到這名義還真的發揮效果，日本因此讓蘇聯大使館的官員(在美國之後)和別連科見面，但對叛逃心知肚明的大使館官員據說對別連科的態度相當不佳<br />\n<br />\n在宣讀老調的「媽媽難過、兒子等爸爸和老婆等丈夫回來」的話一半，就被別連科打斷：「謝謝你的好意，但請你別再浪費唇舌了」，而大使館官員也很識相的喊了聲「叛徒」後氣沖沖地離開。 <br />\n<br />\n確認別連科是真心叛逃蘇聯後，美國總統福特也在9月13日召開國際記者會，公開表示別連科尋求美國的政治庇護<br />\n<br />\n發現紙包不住火的蘇聯則見笑轉生氣，譴責日本破壞國際法和踐踏鄰國之間的關係。"},{"pid":"f23de8f83c1b29fa551edbcf10af2382c4a6d5ec","tid":1016501,"uid":52658,"like":56,"dislike":2,"score":54,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-10T18:37:24.000Z","msg":"MIG-25迫降後不久就被架起臨時圍牆保護不讓外人靠近。 在別連科降落函館後的五個月美國幾乎動員整個國家的專家研究MIG-25<br />\n<br />\n但調查結果卻讓美國人大失所望，原來所謂蘇聯最先進戰機只是極速性能很強大，但整體性能卻只停留下真空管時代的戰機<br />\n<br />\n而且又很諷刺的是，為了應付「幻想中」的MIG-25而推出的F-15「鷹」，在發現MIG-25的落後後，還因此保持幾年「拔劍四海顧茫茫」的狀態<br />\n<br />\n直到被F-15刺激到的蘇聯人推出SU-27後才被打破絕對優勢。 <br />\n<br />\n或許別連科也沒預料到，<span style=\"color: red;\">他的叛逃居然讓美確認自身在冷戰的科技優勢，也讓美國決心拉大與蘇聯的科技與技術優勢，蘇聯也被迫耗費巨資開發下一代戰機</span>，他所造成的擴散影響可說是改變整個冷戰歷史也不為過<br />\n<br />\n但不管是蘇聯還是美國，在很長一段時間都無法滲透別連科叛逃的理由，直到冷戰結束後多年才終於坦承叛逃的理由。 <br />\n<br />\n別連科表示他在蘇聯的第一任妻子實在太過愛慕虛榮和花錢，不僅常要買名貴服裝和去歌劇院，連平常吃的餐點也要高級品才肯入口<br />\n<br />\n儘管在菁英部隊工作的別連科薪水不低，也難以應付妻子的花費<br />\n<br />\n而婚後兩人幾乎是一見面就吵架的狀態，對家庭生活的不滿最終導致他在訓練中決定離開祖國<br />\n<br />\n別連科更形容在離開蘇聯的當下，幾乎有著解脫的快感。<br />\n<br />\n在別連科叛逃的真相公開後，「一個女人扼殺了蘇聯空軍」也就為最佳的時代註解"},{"pid":"2de809c062ad22bac89c011a9bba363fbebd5e9b","tid":1016501,"uid":20419,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-10T18:48:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/smile3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/smile3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/smile3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0eae51e9472586648c9271a808f9b546cf551339","tid":1016501,"uid":52658,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-10T19:01:49.000Z","msg":"推推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c6d6a10e75a1e045b03a146f05429429b7385b73","tid":1016501,"uid":192826,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-10T19:39:17.000Z","msg":"Butterfly effect<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/pig1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3234c4ae34b40144dab55e3d208af86ef5924e50","tid":1016501,"uid":10881,"like":45,"dislike":2,"score":43,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-10T19:39:20.000Z","msg":"驚老婆驚到要背叛國<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7925c936efe70d84db6bde7ecb41df6dadd650f5","tid":1016501,"uid":50801,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3234c4ae34b40144dab55e3d208af86ef5924e50","tid":1016501,"uid":10881,"like":45,"dislike":2,"score":43,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-10T19:39:20.000Z","msg":"驚老婆驚到要背叛國<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-10T19:49:11.000Z","msg":"呢個註腳好正<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"89229c5f2de906c95b630cb98e8c79fcc7d24a03","tid":1016501,"uid":48579,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-10T19:52:47.000Z","msg":"女人累人"},{"pid":"0f7a48e16203224c1f1942bbfac4f75e207b904e","tid":1016501,"uid":157069,"like":5,"dislike":6,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-02-10T20:02:27.000Z","msg":"認真 會唔會單純一個女人<br />\n就搞到佢要拋低自己既屋企人<br />\n同背叛國家去另一個陌生國家<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n理由好牽強<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/pig2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 咁都入女人數"},{"pid":"67638a67aedec2d73d765f3915980cd7ceba7b2d","tid":1016501,"uid":141151,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"7925c936efe70d84db6bde7ecb41df6dadd650f5","tid":1016501,"uid":50801,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3234c4ae34b40144dab55e3d208af86ef5924e50","tid":1016501,"uid":10881,"like":45,"dislike":2,"score":43,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-10T19:39:20.000Z","msg":"驚老婆驚到要背叛國<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-10T19:49:11.000Z","msg":"呢個註腳好正<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-10T20:04:08.000Z","msg":"決定冷戰走向的女人<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f120835569f494b7c337b882d4336d3737fd974e","tid":1016501,"uid":229560,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-10T20:20:13.000Z","msg":"米格25<br />\n果陣美國一直認為要飛得快一定要用釱合金<br />\n所以美國啲戰機研發全部都用又貴又難處理嘅鈦<br />\n以為米格25之所以有辨法飛咁快一定係掌握左鈦合金處理技術<br />\n所以美國果陣好驚，一直好想研發出一種更理想合金<br />\n<br />\n直到呢條友帶著米格25叛逃，美國派人去分解先知原來米格25係用不鏽鋼<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n之後成部機比人研究完再還返比人，上面仲寫左好多Good Very Good<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fb5cb7d54a85187884835bfcc90c689718f2cd77","tid":1016501,"uid":232185,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0f7a48e16203224c1f1942bbfac4f75e207b904e","tid":1016501,"uid":157069,"like":5,"dislike":6,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-02-10T20:02:27.000Z","msg":"認真 會唔會單純一個女人<br />\n就搞到佢要拋低自己既屋企人<br />\n同背叛國家去另一個陌生國家<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n理由好牽強<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/pig2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 咁都入女人數"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-10T20:25:02.000Z","msg":"搵到好少關於佢老婆嘅嘢<br />\n依個link都無<br />\n<a href=\"http://web.archive.org/web/20010111004300/http://fullcontext.org/people/belenko.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fweb.archive.org%2Fweb%2F20010111004300%2Fhttp%3A%2F%2Ffullcontext.org%2Fpeople%2Fbelenko.htm&d=rjg6%2Bw4p6Mv2XY9C6AOo5%2FtobIAPz7vP9zHpdy2ENqg%3D&h=24d3ed1c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://web.archive.org/web/20010111004300/http://fullcontext.org/people/belenko.htm</a>"},{"pid":"3a6bef6b64f8120c1daf0df78a0a59a9aad35247","tid":1016501,"uid":226955,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-10T21:31:15.000Z","msg":"一個八婆加速咗蘇聯倒台嘅歷史進程 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"26fcfe3a7d85cb1659812380eca8649548fd3513","tid":1016501,"uid":59030,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-10T21:41:13.000Z","msg":"鮮為人知<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f95a66336c453b4e56a7f5666c831f38d80336f8","tid":1016501,"uid":130105,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f120835569f494b7c337b882d4336d